description:
Reentrancy in DCA.createOrder(DCA.Order) (src/DCA.sol#38-62):
	External calls:
	- moduleData.args[0] = _resolverModuleArg(address(this),abi.encodeCall(this.checker,(orderId))) (src/DCA.sol#53-56)
	- taskId = _createTask(address(this),abi.encode(this.execute.selector),moduleData,WETH) (src/DCA.sol#60)
		- ops.createTask(_execAddress,_execDataOrSelector,_moduleData,_feeToken) (src/gelato/OpsTaskCreator.sol#51-57)
	State variables written after the call(s):
	- orderToTask[orderId] = taskId (src/DCA.sol#61)
markdown:
Reentrancy in [DCA.createOrder(DCA.Order)](src/DCA.sol#L38-L62):
	External calls:
	- [moduleData.args[0] = _resolverModuleArg(address(this),abi.encodeCall(this.checker,(orderId)))](src/DCA.sol#L53-L56)
	- [taskId = _createTask(address(this),abi.encode(this.execute.selector),moduleData,WETH)](src/DCA.sol#L60)
		- [ops.createTask(_execAddress,_execDataOrSelector,_moduleData,_feeToken)](src/gelato/OpsTaskCreator.sol#L51-L57)
	State variables written after the call(s):
	- [orderToTask[orderId] = taskId](src/DCA.sol#L61)
